    I_Unitable<A_CoordinateCartesian<?>>, I_XMLable, java.lang.Comparable<A_CoordinateCartesian<?>>
    public class CoordinateCartesianRelative
extends A_CoordinateCartesian<CoordinateCartesianRelative>
    Defines the basic elements of arbitrary two-dimensional Cartesian coordinate system for relative coordinates. A relative coordinate resides on the interval [-1,+1] to allow relative positioning from a center origin.
